      *                  * da eseguire                                 *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-scs-cgs-tip-ope    =    01
                     go to qry-let-seq-110
           else if   w-scs-cgs-tip-ope    =    02
                     go to qry-let-seq-140
           else      go to qry-let-seq-900.
