      *                      * Start                                   *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        f-sts                not  = e-not-err
                     go to qry-let-seq-120
           else      go to qry-let-seq-130.
       qry-let-seq-120.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
